Caption.String: Sales tax is taken from the Financial Parameters page.
NOTE: This Land-based Balance of System Cost Model is valid ONLY for land-based installations. Please see Help for details.
Click to apply the cost estimate to the appropriate inputs in the Capital Costs section above.

The balance of system model computes reasonable values for the following inputs based on your project characteristics. You may override the estimated values using the "Inputs" column below and selecting "Use Estimated Value" in the corresponding drop-down menu.

access_roads_cost.Label: Access road and site improvement cost

bos_total_budgeted_cost.Label: Total cost estimate for balance of system

bos_total_cost_per_kw.Label: Balance of system cost per capacity

power_performance_cost.Label: Met mast and power perf. engineering cost

rock_trenching_required.Label: Rock trenching required (% of collector cable length)
